title: Beacon Hill 4BR Duplex for Rent (Both Units!)
posting_body: ['HI!', 'We’re excited to share about our sweet home which is available for rent this coming October 2022.', 'We hope to find a person(s) to live here for a while, who will enjoy our family-friendly neighbors, large yard, garden, and all the pleasures of living on the south-side.', 'Please read this thoroughly, and let us know if there’s anything else we should include, or if you have questions.', 'Thanks!', 'WHAT: Renting our entire home (technically two units); total of four (4) bedrooms, two (2) bathrooms, two (2) kitchens, two (2) living rooms, a front patio space, and a GIANT backyard with a terrace and garden', 'WHERE: Quiet street in Beacon Hill Neighborhood, close to intersection of Beacon Ave S and Orcas, 98108', 'HOW MUCH: $4500 / month (utilities paid for by tenant)', 'FURNISHINGS:', 'The house is unfurnished.', 'TERMS:', 'One time $40 application fee/person (pays for background/credit check), first and last month rent due upon signing + security deposit equal to one months rent (installments available upon request), 1 year lease preferred (or longer), 2-3 references required, monthly income of tenants 2.5x total rent, credit score over 600, no evictions.', 'SPLIT UNIT?', "Yes, it would be easy to treat the entire downstairs unit (which has it's own kitchen/bathroom) as separate if someone in your party desires that kind of separation/privacy.", 'We will NOT be making separate contracts/agreements though.', 'That is up to the tenants to figure out among themselves.', 'OWNER:', 'Who are the homeowners?', 'A couple who lived in Seattle for most of a decade and are now moving home to Montana.', "We're into the outdoors, authentic relating, justice work, design, embodiment, and food.", 'We aim to be responsive to you and any issues with the house.', 'OTHER DEETS:', '- 7000 SF lot (1000 SF interior / floor)', '- AMAZING neighbors who help you, throw parties, and will acknowledge your humanity', '- Large lockable storage shed in backyard', '- Ample off-street parking is available', '- We are a few blocks from Beacon Ave which has frequent busses', '- 1 minute drive to I-5 North on-ramp', '- Walking distance to Georgetown', '- Breezy Town pizza and Flora Bake Shop within walking distance :D', '- Easy drive to grocery (PCC, Safeway, Red Apple)', 'PLEASE TELL US:', '- Some things about yourself; values, interests, hobbies, background, etc?', '- When you hope to move into a new place?', '- What you do for work and where?', '- Your income/credit situation?', '- How many people you plan to have on the lease?', '- Any other question you may have?']
